</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_142" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_142_r2l7">Augſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_142_r2l8"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt Chuncʒ Sarvvurt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l9"><expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> mitburger ſein habe beẏ ew bekumert hab von eins geſcheffts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l10">vvegen / das vorcʒeiten Jobs Rothans <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger beẏ vns getan het das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd daʒ auch </del> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Rate abgeteilt warde / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>vnredlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat recht vnd leuffen niht <expan>cʒugange<ex>n</ex></expan> vvas </del> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l13">daʒ Jr den ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran vveiſen wöllet / daʒ Er dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l14">ſein habe ledig vnd vnbekümert laſſe / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / vnd het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l15"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ derſelb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>cʒeſpr<ex>echen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_142_r2l16"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_142" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Augspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Chuncz Sarwurt,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz im <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> mitburger sein habe bey ew bekumert hab von
                        eins gescheffts wegen, das vorczeiten Jobs Rothans,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, bey uns getan het, das in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate abgeteilt warde.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz er dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sein habe ledig und unbekümert lasse. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>czespr<ex>echen</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
